title: TUESDAY 6/8 -WILL AARON RODGERS SHOW UP TO MINICAMP?
itunes:title: TUESDAY 6/8 -WILL AARON RODGERS SHOW UP TO MINICAMP?
description:
The Packers open minicamp today, but will Aaron Rodgers (0:06) be in attendance? Julio Jones (0:48) arrives in Tennessee. The Ravens extend running back Gus Edwards (1:04) and sign Ja'Wuan James (1:19). Tony Jefferson (1:40) strengthens the 49ers secondary, while Dre Kirkpatrick (1:56) visits the Big Easy. Bruce Arians and Jason Licht (2:15) get rewarded in Tampa, and Michael Gallup (2:40) talks about Dak Prescott's return
